      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "a0041",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "AUTH: catalog GETs 1-3 fully public (browse w/ no token); writes 4-6 need guest JWT (sub='guest', carries table_id).\ncreated_by stays NULL for customer self-orders (set only from staff JWT). Catalog mutations staff-only (manager/admin).",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "AUTH: catalog GETs 1-3 fully public (browse w/ no token); writes 4-6 need guest JWT (sub='guest', carries table_id).\ncreated_by stays NULL for customer self-orders (set only from staff JWT). Catalog mutations staff-only (manager/admin).",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "t101032",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1238,
      "y": 386,
      "width": 644,
      "height": 29,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e293b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 101032,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 101032,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "a0042",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "CACHING: productCacheTTL = 5min (matches FE staleTime → worst-case ~10min staleness). Keys: products/categories/combos/\ntoppings:list + product:<id>. Write-triggered invalidation (invalidateProductCaches...). Redis fail-OPEN → menu survives Redis outage.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CACHING: productCacheTTL = 5min (matches FE staleTime → worst-case ~10min staleness). Keys: products/categories/combos/\ntoppings:list + product:<id>. Write-triggered invalidation (invalidateProductCaches...). Redis fail-OPEN → menu survives Redis outage.",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "t101039",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1238,
      "y": 426,
      "width": 644,
      "height": 29,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e293b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 101039,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 101039,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "a0043",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "ERRORS: bind fail → 400 INVALID_INPUT (respondError). Service → handleServiceError (ErrNotFound→404). FE shows single retry\nstate ('⚠ Kết nối mạng yếu'+Thử lại) for PRODUCTS query only; categories/combos fail silently to [].",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ERRORS: bind fail → 400 INVALID_INPUT (respondError). Service → handleServiceError (ErrNotFound→404). FE shows single retry\nstate ('⚠ Kết nối mạng yếu'+Thử lại) for PRODUCTS query only; categories/combos fail silently to [].",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
