      "frameId": null,
      "text": "⚠ BE FLAGS: (1) GET /products ignores ALL query params — zero c.Query calls, no client filter → tabs/search are no-ops on\nthis branch. (2) No rate-limit MW wired (chain = Logger,Recovery,Metrics; ratelimit.go exists, unused) → Redis cache is the only\npressure valve.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
