      "frameId": null,
      "text": "2 FE shapes: ComboRaw (wire) → Combo (enriched)\nid · category_id NULL SET NULL · name · description NULL→''⚠\nprice int64 · image_path NULL→'' · is_available · sort_order\ncombo_items: [{id, product_id, quantity}] — IDS ONLY\nENRICH (menu/page.tsx:86-105 useMemo): join ComboRaw\nvs ['products-all'] → names/prices/toppings · missing→raw UUID\ncombo_items = STATIC template; expanded at order time",
