      "index": "a004v",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "▓ order_cache_<id>  (localStorage)  → 'what is order X?'  (many coexist)\n▓ activeOrderId     (cart store, partialize) → 'which am I following?' (exactly one)\n▓ <id> in the URL   → shareable / reloadable\nHANDOFF on 201 (3 writes): ① order_cache_<id>=JSON(order) ② setActiveOrderId(id) ③ clearCart()\nthen router.replace('/order/<id>')  (replace not push → back-button can't re-submit)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "▓ order_cache_<id>  (localStorage)  → 'what is order X?'  (many coexist)\n▓ activeOrderId     (cart store, partialize) → 'which am I following?' (exactly one)\n▓ <id> in the URL   → shareable / reloadable\nHANDOFF on 201 (3 writes): ① order_cache_<id>=JSON(order) ② setActiveOrderId(id) ③ clearCart()\nthen router.replace('/order/<id>')  (replace not push → back-button can't re-submit)",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
