      "index": "a0054",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "useOrderSSE(params.id) 3 phases:\nt0 read ▓cache → instant paint (no spinner)\nt2 GET /orders/:id authoritative (404→'không tìm thấy')\nt3 SSE /orders/:id/events deltas patch in place\nSSE relays Redis pub/sub ONLY, no initial snapshot → must REST-seed\nreconnect: expo backoff, max 5, banner after 3\nALL 3 write back to ▓ order_cache (self-refresh loop)\nfork buttons: Theo dõi · follow toggle · Đặt thêm món · Huỷ đơn",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "useOrderSSE(params.id) 3 phases:\nt0 read ▓cache → instant paint (no spinner)\nt2 GET /orders/:id authoritative (404→'không tìm thấy')\nt3 SSE /orders/:id/events deltas patch in place\nSSE relays Redis pub/sub ONLY, no initial snapshot → must REST-seed\nreconnect: expo backoff, max 5, banner after 3\nALL 3 write back to ▓ order_cache (self-refresh loop)\nfork buttons: Theo dõi · follow toggle · Đặt thêm món · Huỷ đơn",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
