      "text": "loadCachedOrders() scans ALL ▓ order_cache_* keys\nparses each, sorts newest-first\nshows status/progress from snapshots detail page persisted\nfilters combo headers (combo_id && !combo_ref_id)\nprogress = Σ qty_served / Σ quantity\n'Xoá lịch sử' removes ALL order_cache_* keys\ncached object = full Order (id·order_number·status·\n  source·table_name·total_amount·items[])",
