      "index": "a005j",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "items/tableId/tableName : ░ cart memory   F5❌ newdev❌   /menu only, pre-POST\norder_cache_<id> : ▓ localStorage   F5✅ newdev❌   /order/<id> + /order list\nactiveOrderId : ▓ cart store persisted   F5✅ newdev❌   /tracking pointer\norder id : the URL   F5✅ newdev✅   /order/<id>, ?add_to_order=     |     the order row : BE MySQL+Redis   F5✅ newdev✅   every page, every device",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "items/tableId/tableName : ░ cart memory   F5❌ newdev❌   /menu only, pre-POST\norder_cache_<id> : ▓ localStorage   F5✅ newdev❌   /order/<id> + /order list\nactiveOrderId : ▓ cart store persisted   F5✅ newdev❌   /tracking pointer\norder id : the URL   F5✅ newdev✅   /order/<id>, ?add_to_order=     |     the order row : BE MySQL+Redis   F5✅ newdev✅   every page, every device",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
