      "originalText": "1 · Route navigation → ShopLoading\n   centered orange spinner, whole (shop) shell (h-8 w-8 ring, animate-spin, border-t-orange-500). Not menu-specific.\n2 · MenuPage mounts → <Suspense> fallback (EMPTY) wraps MenuContent (for useSearchParams suspend; route spinner covers it)\n3 · MenuContent → 4 useQuery fire; only 'products' drives visible skeleton",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
