      "seed": 101627,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 101627,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "a006f",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "COMBO EXPLODE (POST /orders): 1 orders row + N order_items. Combo = ₫0 HEADER (product_id null, combo_id set, combo_ref_id null)\n+ sub-items (product_id set, combo_ref_id→header, real template prices). canh = own STANDALONE row, never inside combo.\ntotal_amount DERIVED: RecalculateTotalAmount = SUM(unit_price×quantity) → 0·1+9000·1+4000·3+0·1 = ₫21,000, denormalized,\nre-run after EVERY item mutation (OC-epic bug: priced header double-counted). No status/flagged/filling on order_items —\nitem progress = qty_served vs quantity · nhân in toppings_snapshot (frozen JSON, not FK). Empty string → NULL via nullStr().",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "COMBO EXPLODE (POST /orders): 1 orders row + N order_items. Combo = ₫0 HEADER (product_id null, combo_id set, combo_ref_id null)\n+ sub-items (product_id set, combo_ref_id→header, real template prices). canh = own STANDALONE row, never inside combo.\ntotal_amount DERIVED: RecalculateTotalAmount = SUM(unit_price×quantity) → 0·1+9000·1+4000·3+0·1 = ₫21,000, denormalized,\nre-run after EVERY item mutation (OC-epic bug: priced header double-counted). No status/flagged/filling on order_items —\nitem progress = qty_served vs quantity · nhân in toppings_snapshot (frozen JSON, not FK). Empty string → NULL via nullStr().",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "t101634",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1818,
      "y": 1741,
      "width": 144,
      "height": 16,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#0f172a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 101634,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 101634,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "a006g",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "CANH & NHÂN mechanism:",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CANH & NHÂN mechanism:",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "t101641",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1818,
      "y": 1759,
      "width": 664,
      "height": 69,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e293b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 101641,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 101641,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "a006h",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "NHÂN (thịt/mộc nhĩ) = ₫0 TOPPING, not a field (mig016 added filling, 017 dropped). Cart toppings[] → topping_ids[] →\n  buildToppingsSnapshot freezes {id,name,price} into toppings_snapshot. Combo applies its nhân to every non-canh sub-item.\nCANH = real ₫0 product NEVER inside a combo. Stable ids canh_<id>_rau / canh_<id>_plain · setCanhQty upsert (qty0=remove).\n  Stripped from combo_items (isSoupName) → own row. BE treats supplied combo_items as COMPLETE list (overrides replace\n  template) so canh never re-expands. Session-only (partialize never writes canh; migrate flushes legacy counter).",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "NHÂN (thịt/mộc nhĩ) = ₫0 TOPPING, not a field (mig016 added filling, 017 dropped). Cart toppings[] → topping_ids[] →\n  buildToppingsSnapshot freezes {id,name,price} into toppings_snapshot. Combo applies its nhân to every non-canh sub-item.\nCANH = real ₫0 product NEVER inside a combo. Stable ids canh_<id>_rau / canh_<id>_plain · setCanhQty upsert (qty0=remove).\n  Stripped from combo_items (isSoupName) → own row. BE treats supplied combo_items as COMPLETE list (overrides replace\n  template) so canh never re-expands. Session-only (partialize never writes canh; migrate flushes legacy counter).",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "t101648",
      "type": "text",
