      "index": "a006i",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "PEAK 12:04 — 8 open orders on KDS · day revenue 21+150+60+27+0+30+60+12 = ₫360,000 (Bàn 05 cancel excluded).\nRealtime: guest SSE (Bearer header) item_progress/status/completed · KDS+admin WS (?token) new_order×8 → setQueryData(['orders','live']).\nCaching: L1 TanStack 5min + L2 Redis 5min fail-open + L3 MySQL · /menu ISR revalidate=300 + HydrationBoundary (zero spinner) ·\norders NEVER cached (pushed). Monitoring: /metrics→Prometheus:9090, logs→Promtail→Loki:3100, Grafana:3001 (2 alerts:\nHighErrorRate 5xx>5%, SlowResponseTime p95>500ms).",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PEAK 12:04 — 8 open orders on KDS · day revenue 21+150+60+27+0+30+60+12 = ₫360,000 (Bàn 05 cancel excluded).\nRealtime: guest SSE (Bearer header) item_progress/status/completed · KDS+admin WS (?token) new_order×8 → setQueryData(['orders','live']).\nCaching: L1 TanStack 5min + L2 Redis 5min fail-open + L3 MySQL · /menu ISR revalidate=300 + HydrationBoundary (zero spinner) ·\norders NEVER cached (pushed). Monitoring: /metrics→Prometheus:9090, logs→Promtail→Loki:3100, Grafana:3001 (2 alerts:\nHighErrorRate 5xx>5%, SlowResponseTime p95>500ms).",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
