      "text": "INGREDIENTS: stock NOT auto-decremented on cook — only manual stock_movements (out floors at GREATEST(0, stock-qty)).\nproduct_ingredients recipe link exists but nothing reads it during order flow. Badges: 0=out_of_stock · ≤min=low_stock · within 7d=expiring_soon.",
